		{"id":"9e09ccc68c5ecd2c","type":"text","text":"### Product Leadership 🧑‍💻\nGOAL\n- Product is aligned to business vision and strategy\n- Investment is allocated correctly across teams and focus areas","x":-345,"y":400,"width":296,"height":235,"color":"6"},
