		{"id":"4fc262ab47f5aa79","type":"text","text":"- Evangelizing the roadmap an advocating the priorities\n- Explaining the assumptions, tests, data\n- Minimizing high-integrity committments","x":75,"y":77,"width":250,"height":243,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"c3f24daf6b380243","type":"text","text":"- Talking to stakeholders to find out what they need\n- What's important to you\n- What must this do to satisfy your constraints\n- How would you see this working if you could wave a magic want","x":885,"y":240,"width":250,"height":280,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"6a7b7d0c7280dd10","type":"text","text":"- Interviews\n- Synthesizing new information into existing models\n- Finding opportunities\n- Validating and quantifying problems\n- Validation solutions with people\n- Sharing learnings\n- Evangelizing continuous discovery","x":45,"y":-760,"width":250,"height":350,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"0cd455197dd49cc6","type":"text","text":"- Designing small tests of assumptions and ideas\n- Evangelizing experimentation\n- Make decisions\n- Validating and quantifying problems\n- Review learnings\n- Maintain map of problems/opportunities","x":660,"y":-730,"width":250,"height":330,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"945b3065a85413c0","type":"text","text":"### Engineering Lead 🧑‍💻\nGOAL\n- Quality software\n- Scalable architecture","x":1170,"y":127,"width":290,"height":213,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"5a2f57111e900ef7","type":"text","text":"- Breaking work into it's valuable parts\n- Connecting goals to strategy\n- Ordering and sequencing","x":1540,"y":127,"width":250,"height":213,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"413d8a23d7c3df2f","type":"text","text":"- Identifying and minimizing dependencies\n- De-risking and testing\n- Incorporating feedback\n- Prioritization","x":2000,"y":-636,"width":250,"height":213,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"ff917e72c486f04b","type":"text","text":"\n- Business logic\n- Telemetry and instrumentation\n- User workflows\n- UI mockups and designs","x":2000,"y":200,"width":250,"height":213,"color":"1"},
